<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Hi <%= @user.name%>,
    <p>
    <% if @time_change and @location_change %>
        The following changes have been made to your section:
    <% else %>
        The following change has been made to your section:
    <% end %>
    <ul>
    <% if @time_change and @time_default_change %>
        <li><b>The default time of your section has been changed to ... . You will now be meeting at that time from here on out.</b></li>
    <% elsif @time_change %>
        <li><b>Your section's time has been temporarily changed to ... . <i>This is only a temporary change for your next meeting.</i></b></li>
    <% end %>
    <% if @location_change and @location_default_change %>
        <li><b>The default location of your section has been changed to ... . You will now be meeting there from here on out.</b></li>
    <% elsif @location_change %>
        <li><b>Your section's location has been temporarily changed to ... . <i>This is only a temporary change for your next meeting.</i></b></li>
    <% end %>
    </ul>
    <p>If you have any concerns, please let your mentor know!</p>
    Best,<br>
    CSM
  </body>
</html>